room_title: Escape room "The Psycho Killer" by Boulder Escape Room in Longmont
room_description: You have been trapped by the Psycho Killer! This particular psycho is a fiend for puzzles. He has meticulously set up a game of logic that challenges your mental stamina and your ability to work with others. Now you must solve riddles, find clues, and outsmart the psycho killer before time runs out...
